\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the mistress supervise all the work personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, 'cos of - chiefly the children you see and chiefly nurse maid with the children - chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You were really helping with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, with the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you have preferred another type of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
