\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I enjoyed it because there was just a start from home you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You didn't have any training for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Or for any other job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. Well, if it - the next time - place following on would expect me - would come in to that there. 'Cos that was only a start you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 After you left school you went to work during the day and lived at home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Slept at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When you started full time work did it change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Or with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
