\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, it - I used to go to chapel the same and - but never with them you see - no - I only had - yes -
