\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
That I don't know - whether they - went out together or not - they led their lives - they didn't interest me as to what they were going to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What was Colonel Anderson's occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, he was retired Colonel, he didn't do anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was he in the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
He - yes he was retired from the Army. He came - I don't know where he came from to Manor Road but they went abroad that's how they ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 She was a woman they always called on for when they entertained. I never washed up and that 'cos I was cooking and all, I couldn't do it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And would they have dinner parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. They had dinner parties. That's when the woman used to come over to wash up and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You had a lot of work to do - did you have to wait at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, I took the - they waited on themselves the ones that was in there you see, they didn't have it - waited on - I took - would take the food in - they'd help themselves you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You don't know what kind of people your employers friends were at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, I don't know anything about their private life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would they be the same class as their master and mistress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I should think so - I don't know really - I couldn't - vouch on what their friends were you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What sort of class would you say that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, they - he was - he was a Colonel up until - I couldn't tell you anything about him like - he was a Colonel from the Army - and I suppose he would be a retired Colonel because he was home you see - he wasn't away then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was the mistress the same sort of person as the master - in the same class as his?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, I - I don't know - she wasn't in the services - she wasn't in services is that what you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, I meant was she the same sort of education and social standing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh, I couldn't tell you that. I mean I didn't know their private - they didn't converse with me - their private life you see. I was a servant and they were them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you remember what the behaviour of the guests were towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, they were always all right to me.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the master and mistress treat some of their friends differently from others? With more elaborate entertainment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I think - oh no, they 
were all - if they had a dinner party they had a dinner party, but it was all average - the same sort of thing - soup, fish and pudding - soup, fish and meat and pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you think your master and mistress were content with their station in life or do you think they would have liked a higher position?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh, I couldn't say nothing about - they never - they never conversed me as to their private life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Had you known people like them before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did you think of them and their way of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well - I liked them very much - they were very nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did their manners and general behaviour seem different from people you had associated with before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, they were very - they were the average people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I think you told me you were twenty-eight when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How long had you known your husband then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Er - about three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How did you meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, while I was at Manor Lodge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 At church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. He - he - th
ey had - well, see my husbands father was the coal merchants at Stouton and he was the only coal merchant. Well, my husband used to drive one of the coal lorries and - the - but one day when he was out the - it was a slippery day and the - he - in getting
 
up to the lorry he touched the - he had the tall horse - he touched the tail in getting up and the horse bolted and school was about coming out and my husband held onto the reins as long as he could and then dropped them and the wheel went over his leg - 
h
e was in hospital then for nine months. And dear old Doctor Broder - the hospital sent him out with an open wound - he wanted to - he - they wanted to take his leg off you see but - Doctor Broder said - oh wonderful doctor - he said - I think he said if y
ou have it privately treated I can guarantee to save that leg. And he had the leg up 'til his - the day he died. Never had his leg off. Wonderful doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Who?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Your husband. Was he a Guildford family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh he was Guildford - you see, number of years in Guildford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you save up money before getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did your parents help you in setting up a home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, no, we fought for ourselves in those days - we didn't expect our parents to
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh only about a twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 About a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Could you describe the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 at Stoughton church - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have some wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Er - well, just a few you see from - small affair - didn't - you see my people were up in the midland then you see, I told you, they'd left this part and they - well not - they had only a few year there 'cos they were getting oh you see, but that's w
here they finished at - their life at - \{ILLEGIBLE\}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 But you had some presents and some guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh yes, we had presents - we didn't have big guest and party like - we went up to London and spent out evening in London and we had - just had some friends for - that went to the church and see us }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  and came home and made the tea and then we went up to London and that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So that was your honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that was our.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You didn't stay in London?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, oh no. And I went in my house the fortnight to the day I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 . It was up North Road - I was in that cottage for twenty years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 This was the house you lived in when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 - where we went. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1653738\charrsid10685554 Well, the landlord was Mr Fork - he - was
 the optician in the town - and we - it was funny how we got the house 'cos we went in for about a fortnight with the old people you see and then he come home - in the meanwhile - he was then in Dennis's because you see - the struggle of his leg 'he got a
ll out before we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1653738\charrsid10685554  'cos it was before we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1653738\charrsid10685554  when he had the accident - and he was forty-six years in Dennis's - yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
And - we - he came home one morning and he says oh there's a house going he said - will be going he said up North Road 
so he give me the name of one of the fellows that told him and I went about it and he said I don't think there's anybody going. I said well, he is going. Well, in the meanwhile they'd sent the key - he was a moonlighter as they called them - somebody that
 hopped out you see, and the key had been sent through the post and I had a letter to say would I come down to see them and I got a house straight away.
