\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  - Dennis's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did he do in Dennis's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 He was - a - what do you call them - the engine - mechanic, you see on the machines - mech - machinists really then - have it that way.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Then did he have another job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. Forty-six years he was there - he retired from Dennis's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did he have any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How do you think your husband felt about his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, he liked his work - the money them days were very small you know 
- fourpence ha'penny an hour - twenty-six shillings a week was what he earned. You can't credit it can you. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did he like it to do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. He was there forty-six years that proves he liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you work after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh I worked from the time I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  'til I was - drew my pension. I either worked or had in lodgers. I - I - I either went out to work or had lodgers. Now, I come under the five year plan with the insurance which - made me - fifty - sixty-two
 before I could draw my pension because my five years wasn't up but in between that time - if I hadn't got lodgers - other work - there was always something I was doing - office cleaning or something and then I done London Clinical work with mothers and b
abies - yes - I had mothers and babies - oh - how many summers - all the time - 'cos my first one was born under the twelve month, I had two in eighteen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1653738\charrsid10685554  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 months - children - one boy and one girl - and then - while they were young and tiny instead of taking m
en lodgers or going out to work I had the mothers and babies from London Clinic. And I did that with - Marylebone Clinic and it - Mrs Shaw was the lady's name that always worked - took on with me. Her son was a doctor. And I did that for some years - I ha
d
 mothers and babies and how I managed then - my husband used to sleep in the boys room and I was left in the girls room which always - always gave up with the one bedroom. Well, we had to do something for a living. You see you couldn't live on that money 
could you - I had to pull my weight right - all my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  life 'til I drew my pension.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And you had two children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Two children - yes. Two in eighteen months - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Can you remember when they were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well, 1915 - 1916 - let me see - I - '16 - and I'd be the end of 1916 the first.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was that the boy or the girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 That was the boy - wait a minute - let's get it right - the girl was the youngest - it's the boy first - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When was the ....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 The girl would be - there was two in eighteen months that's how I can work out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So she would be born in 1917?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 It was too quick - the old doctor - yes - Doctor Broder said no more of this because he - he brought them himself into the world.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were they born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. They was - see you didn't go away in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you know what to expect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, no only what you used to talk about you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How did you get on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Very well, but of course I was so small - couldn't bring them you see. Do
ctor Broder brought them - Doctor Broder brought them into the world himself. And he said, no more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you mean by that that he had to use forceps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. To save me having operation in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You didn't have an operation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, they - what he did was use the forceps to force them - them into the world. I couldn't bring them myself, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did your husband help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. I had a - you see you had a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I mean help with the babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, he never did anything when they were young like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How soon were you out of bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, you - was a different way of having babies then to what it is now. I - you had to stay in bed for a fortnight. I was in bed for a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And then after a fortnight would you be up for the whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh - yes, you'd get up and - you'd have somebody to do the work for a time. I had to anyway - I did and some people wouldn't but - I had to have a - a woman you see to - for a time, I couldn't say now how many months was 
it - but - several months you see because - having a bad time you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would that be a relation or a neighbour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, that was a person outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You employed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. And she slept in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And you had a nurse did you to help you with the baby?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. No - Doctor Broder managed himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And did the nurse come in afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, 'cos the woman did you see. She was - she used to go out doing that sort of thing you see. She'd bath the baby and do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So she stayed with you and looked after the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that's right. She stayed and slept in for three weeks and then she'd come occasionally, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 That was for about a couple of months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the nurse look after the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh y
es, she was very - not - outside nurse - the woman. Yes. You see, they were different these - they didn't - you didn't have nurses like you've got today every life is different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did the woman do for the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, she'd bath it and feed it and do every thing, you see - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you feed the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was that because you had such a bad time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 The doctor advised you not to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Hadn't strength you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So the baby was bottle fed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Bottle fed both of them. Brought up and fed on boiled milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If the baby was asleep would you wake it for a feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, never. Let them sleep on their time out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have any difficulties in feeding the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If you needed advice who would you ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, I don't know as - well, this woman you see, she was only in next door this woman - she went out. She lived next door to me she. She was very handy you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If the baby was asleep would you wake if for a feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, I would never wake a child if it were asleep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If it cried before the normal time would you feed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, depended what the time was - if I thought it was long enough for the child to be hungry - yes, I would feed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What would you do if it didn't seem hungry?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well - you see, what can I say to that - I don't know ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you try to force it to take the bottle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Not if it - not if it wasn't feeding time near 'cos I think it gives them indigestion if they - you feed out of the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you remember how long you let it go on feeding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No, well, you see there weren't so much of this timing, I can't - you can't - count those days with these you see really with - babies and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When did you give it its first solid food - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Soon as they could take it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And when would you wean the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Er - well - on the average - eleven months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you do it suddenly or gradually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Gradually. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the baby get upset - did it mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you think it did any harm to a baby to let it cry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, I - I don't think you should let a child cry unnecessary unless you should certainly try to find out what the child was crying for - wouldn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you punish it when it was naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. Not in - not as a young child. Not 'til they were old enough to understand what that meant.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How much did your husband have to do with your children when they were babies under a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And you fed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Bathed them, changed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, did everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Played with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Got them to sleep - attended to them during the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes - everything - yes. He had his job and he said one job for me. He said wait 'til they grow up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You were telling me that you had to work in order to supplement the housekeeping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you know how much your husband earned in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, when he started it was twenty-six shil
lings a week. Yes. Twenty-six shillings a - out of that he had to have his smoking money or his pint as he called it or - anything - and the rent and we had to live and I never owed anybody for a penny.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How much of that would he give to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 We
ll, of course the beer - what was the beer - tuppence a pint - and cigarettes was oh I don't know - tuppence a packet was it - I think so somewhere along there. Well I think I would get fifteen shillings - round about - either fifteen to a pound.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 To feed your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
To do the lot - six shillings a week rent and then - but you could get a joint for about a couple of shillings in them days, you know. You see everything was so - different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you discuss with your husband how the money should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. He went to his club and that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How many rooms were there in your cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Six - six rooms. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were there any relatives or lodgers living with you - you did have some people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I had lodgers when - I could
 have them. You see - before the children came - I had lodgers. When the children came I felt my job at home is with the children - and I've got to do something to counteract for the - get the money in with - look after the children at the same time so I 
did London Clinic work for several - some years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So mothers came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Mothers came all through the summer with their babies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And so they paid you money for living in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 They paid - no, they didn't - come from London. You see, Mrs Shaw sent it from the London ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 But they did their own work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, they - no, they went out with the children - I did the work. And they'd go out in the morning - take their babies and go out in the morning. And then I would go out with th
em in the afternoon - I'd do the work - and they'd go in the morning. And I'd go out with them and mine you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 In the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. That's what we'd do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So did you have any paid help at that time to help you with the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. No pay - no money them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about the washing? Was it done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. I - when I was able to do my own washing I did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Otherwise if you couldn't do it would it be sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well, a neighbour would do it you see. You a
lways had good kind neighbours in those days - you haven't got them today. You see, the people are selfish today - they live for themselves.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you make any of your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh I did everything - made everything - yes. Made all the children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 
\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 s clothes and made all the babies clothes - I did everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And what about your husband - did he mend anything for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Nothing like that. So you made the clothes yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, I made everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have any secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. There was no secondhand business in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about shoes - you had to buy shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, I'd buy shoes - and mended them myself. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did your husband do to help you in the house - did he do any cleaning - cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. Wonder -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 He did one thing - Dennis's and nothing else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, I did them myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You said that you did everything for the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So if he didn't have time to help with their dressing or give them a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, he was going to work. You, see, they used to go at six o'clock in the morning in those days - 
he was - remember the war was on - there was the 1914-18 war and - we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 in '15 - there was three years of war you see. You can't - you got to - allow for all that - he had good long hours at Dennis's. That's when his money began to rise - not wh
en he first went there but the hours he put in you see, he - it - really was .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would he read to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. Nothing - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Or tell them stories?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, he had nothing for them in that way;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Or take them out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. He had no time for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Or look after them when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No. When he'd done his work he'd go to his club for an hours recreation and so on - that was it - up in the morning and work at six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did your children help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh
, when they were old enough - yes. Usually Alfred the boy used to go up and down with the babies out in the back - oh he was a good boy for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 He had regular tasks to do did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. He'd - well he was fond of the babies he was - he used to l
ike these London babies and he'd go about - mind you he wouldn't look at Margie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What time did the children go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh their time averaged six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And would they put themselves to bed or would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh, I - it depend on their a
ge that you see. But - if they were old enough to put themselves - I never nursed children, you know when their old enough to be made to do things they got to do it. I was about them the same as I was brought up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did they share a bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Not a bed. The room - they had their own beds because it's save shifting walking one another up you see, they each had their own bed.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How did you manage when you had your visitors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, we - I had the one room given up just the same - as I give to the lodgers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So you and your husband had one room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, no. Er - my husband went in the boys room and I went in the girls room, see. Had to give}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 up one bedroom entirely - for lodgers or for London mothers and babies. But of course all the time they wer
e little I had London mothers and babies 'cos my place was with my children. And I had to - bring - have bring in money from somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Where did you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Out in the scullery - in a - in a big galvanised bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well, every night I had to have a bath - I used to light the copper for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 A special day in the week would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, any night in the week when they wanted a bath for they were out all - a bath was necessary they were in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When did the children have clean clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh whenever they was dirty - I never had a dither about clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did they always have clean clothes after a bath?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well, naturally enough you wouldn't put the same vest on them when you bathed them would you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Can you tell me where you had your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh in the kitchen - when - yes - always in the kitchen. You see the houses in those days were different than they are these - you'd get front room, kitchen and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 scullery}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  you called it - today there are posher ideas for every }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 accommodation}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well they often have a sort of kitchen breakfast room don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would there be any occasions when you'd have your meal in a different room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Not necessary. Always in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And where did you cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 In the scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And what with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Gas cooker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When was breakfast - what time did you have breakfast in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And would your husband be there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, he used to go to work at six in those days and come home to breakfast at half past eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How did he manage for his first meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 He didn't have a meal in - before he went to work - only a drink - cup of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And what did you usually eat and drink at breakfast time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, we had cereals and then - done eggs and bacon or - whatever I could get. Depends how the money runs - you got to think in those days - my husband started with twenty-six shillings a week wages.
 Then we had to pay six shillings rent out of that - he had to have his pocket money and the rest - remainder we had to live on. That's why I always had the work or take lodgers or go out to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have anything different on certain days such as Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, we always had a joint on a Sunday. You'd get a joint for about a couple of shillings in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And what about Sunday evening - would you have the same sort of meal as you'd have on a week day or would it be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No - we averaged the same - meals most days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you have a special tea on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. Nothing special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What would you have for your ordinary mid-day meal in the week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, we - far - depended as far as the meat went - whether we
 - I had a made up dish or whether we had a - you know - something like liver or something of that. But - on the average - mostly in the week it was made up dishes of something or other. You, see - the war was on in those days - and - my husband couldn't 
d
o without potatoes and we were rationed with potatoes and I used to put the two babies in the pram and come to Guildford from Stoughton and walk to Guildford to get him his potatoes for dinner every day - and we were only - rationed at a pound of potatoes
 so that me and the children used to have boiled puddings and that sort of thing - so kept - kept all the potatoes for father - to work on - you see, he couldn't have - he hadn't a meal if he didn't have his potatoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did you have in the evening then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, just a drink of coffee or something like that - cocoa or coffee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Anything to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, bit of bread and cheese perhaps. The children didn't have anything after tea. They were - they used to go to bed about - between half past five and six. That was my time to put them to bed when they were young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever make your own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, I used to make jam when the - we did have a few fruit bushes in the garden and I picked the fruit the
n and made the jam. You see, the sugar was only about three ha'pence a pound then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, my husband was very fond of pickled onions, I used to do a lot of those - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You never made wine or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Any sort of herbal medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. No. We didn't have - the only medicines we took if you were out of sorts were - sulphur and treacle. I think I told you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I think you used to have that at your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Yes. We had it - and I gave it to my 
children. And - Doctor Broder always said to me - he was a - an American doctor - but a wonderful doctor - and he was so clever - and he said to me he brought my two children in the world you see - in those days - you got an ordinary mid-wife you see, you
 
didn't necessary have to have qualified people for a birth - but I had to because of being so small. And he used to say to me now he says you take a quarter of a teaspoonful of Epsom salts in your first cup of tea of a morning and - it will keep the blood
stream going and do you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 I've taken that for over fifty years. Yes. A quarter of a teaspoonful in my first cup of tea - and he always said it kept the blood clean. He was wonderful - oh he was a wonderful doctor. 'Cos he's been dead many years now. He w
ent down to Hove - he took his housekeeper - he went to Hove and then he retired and went down there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about bottled fruit - did you bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, no, I only made it more in jam because I tell you it - you could make 
jam tarts or - roly-poly and all that sort of thing which was more useful than a bottle of fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about your vegetables and fruit that you had at home - would you have to buy them or would you grow them yourself?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, we did grow a few po
tatoes in the garden but - not enough to last the year round, you see. That was after the war - 'cos we were rationed on a lot of thing you know. The four years of the war - 'cos you see that was '14 to '18 and we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  in '15 so that gives three - still three years of war to contend with
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, I not - I didn't go in for tinned stuff with the children I gave them wholesome fruit - or whatever I could get from the shops.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about livestock - did you have any hens or pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, no, they were - the garden wasn't big enough to take animals and I didn't think it was healthy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, ever day if I could get it. Used to depend on how
 your money run. A lot of it - you had to go according you see - 'cos I told you money was very small - I had very little to do on in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you buy tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. You could get - now for - at the butchers in those days - you could 
get sixpennyworth of pieces a pennyworth of suet and - you could make a lovely meat pudding for a family with that. You couldn't realize it today could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about extra meat - did you ever get any from poaching from rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Occasionally my husband have had a rabbit given to him and - and by neighbour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would that be very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No. Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And would that be from a friend at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever have to go short yourself so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No, because in the time when the struggle was on with the doctors and the bills and things he said to me - never worry he said all I think about is life not money. And he said if I never get - but he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 knew}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554  he would get it - he said I won'
t worry. So, of course I had two children in eighteen months and that meant a doctors bill each time you see - because it isn't like - you can't compare those days to now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have enough to eat yourself? Or did you sometimes go short?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh ye
s - no, I didn't go short because I - I've always been very methodical in my cooking and I - I believed in a lot of boiled rice because that's - very wholesome thing for young people - used to have a lot of boiled rice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about table manners for your children - were they allowed to talk during meal
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Certainly not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were they allowed to choose what they wanted to eat from what was cooked or did they have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 They had to have what was put before them and eat that or nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Supposing they left some food uneaten on the plate - what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh they wouldn't do it 'cos they know they didn't dare. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If they did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 They would have it for tea. They'd got to eat it because it was good wholesome food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 It would come again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Yes, it would come up again. And then I think I told you in those days - I took mothers and babies because my children were young and I - that was - help in the home as well as other things you see. And I went to w
ork and had lodgers and - or went out to work when they went to school - but before school age I had London mothers and babies and I did London Clinic work for some years and - Mrs Shaw - it was Marylebone clinic - and - yes, yes, well I did that for year
s to help the home going you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Supposing your children wanted something on the table like the salt were they allowed to ask for it or did they have to wait until it was offered to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, no, they - if there was anything that - that they p
articularly wanted I would give it them if I thought it was necessary they should have it. Or it was good for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Could they have a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. I would give them plenty of fruit and that you know whilst they was growing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were they taught to hold their knife and fork in a certain way and sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, they did that from early birth - they was taught that you see they grew into that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You taught them when they were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, very young I taught them - manners and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were they allowed to bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And when could they leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When they'd had their meal if they asked permission to get down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When would 
the other members of the family - the grown ups - leave - would they wait til the end or would they leave the table when they were finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, they'd leave when they'd finished you see but if - if the children wanted to go and they asked permission they could go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did all the family sit at the table together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And did they have regular places and sit at the same place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, yes, I think they all chaired their own place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Who would serve the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Me. I'd serve everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And in what order would you serve them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, not in particular order - perhaps some - sometimes I might begin with the youngest or begin with the oldest - just all depends.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You wouldn't always serve your husband first - or would he come first and then the children afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, he - he - he joined in but perhaps I would have to start the meal before he came in you see because of the children getting to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 But if was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If he was there he would be served first because he would only have so long for his dinner you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When the children were too young to feed themselves would they be fed at the table or would they be fed beforehand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, I generally fed them beforehand becaus
e I can put a block on serving of the others you see if they were too young I used to - they used to have boiled bread as baby you see don't hear of such things today because it was a special bread in those days that you could boil up what they call bread
 pap for the baby, you see, you could do in those days but you couldn't do with the bread today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When did they join in the family meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, as soon as they was old enough to sit to the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And feed themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, and feed themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When your children were young did you feel that there was a right and wrong way of bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Definite - I thought - I bought them the way I was taught myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you and your husband have the same ideas about bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 He never interfered with it - bringing of the children. I ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever discuss it with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, not really because - I think he hadn't the same quite interest you see as I had and the children had to be brought up the sam
e as I was brought up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was there anyone you used to talk to if you were worried about the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No. I didn't - there was nobody particular that I had to - enquire - ask questions about the children because I knew how to manage them - I knew 
what they needed and if they wanted medicine I knew what to give them and so on - I never bothered anybody I just ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You managed yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. Always managed myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was your mother alive when your children were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No I was trying to work that out - see they were - that's puzzling ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did she ever come down to visit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No, well, you see I was living Stoughton when my children were born - oh yes, that's right - now I've got it - you see that's what plays me about 
- that's why I wanted them - yes, they did come to Guildford when my children were small. 'Cos the latter part of their life they were living in Malvern in the Midlands. See, and my dad came to Guildford and up at Shepherds Hill when I was - when he was -
 eight - over eighty years of age when he came down from the Midlands and stayed for a holiday with me.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How often would you see her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh not very often. About once in two or three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever ask her advice in bringing up your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, because I - I was so - brought myself - 'cos I knew how to manage you see - I didn't need any advice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have the same ideas as she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, oh yes, my ideas was firmness and - and - proper manners and everything like that. A
s a child should be brought up, and I think I told you there was always the cane hanging over the picture. My dad was very strict - but he - he wasn't cruel - he was a wonderful man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about your mother-in-law - did you see much of her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was she alive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, she wasn't alive - I don't - I don't remember - I've no recollection of that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Can you tell me some of the things you felt you ought to do for your children? Did you feel it was important that they should have affect
ion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, and they should mix - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 They should mix with other children you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about safety?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, they were always taught that you see, to be careful road crossing and climbing trees and that which mine did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about food? Did you feel you ought to be careful what sort-of diet you gave them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
No, there was nothing particular - they could eat anything. Nothing - nothing to worry about their food. They were healthy children - they could eat anything
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 But you told me you thought it was important they should have some discipline?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh definitely, definitely. And then that now - none of my children would back answer me now - not my boy or my girl will answer - I'm really past the children of t
oday because I've never been used to it and you see they've got no affection for the parents they - they don't have the discipline or anything that mine had and the children wouldn't say - if they thought their mother wanted it - oh she shouldn't have it 
and all that sort of - you would never hear anything of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you want them to share their worries with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, I don't know as they had any - they - they were - ordinary children you know - they entered into everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 How did you want them to behave towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, as I've told you they had to have - discipline and know their parents and treat their parents as they should do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When the children were young did you and your husband ever manage to leave them so you could go out together?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Never left - I'd never turn the key on my dear children - never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did anyone come in to look after them for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I didn't leave them - I was always there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Not even a relation or neighbour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, you see, my husba
nd would be in of an evening you see, if I went out for an evening. And I took them with me in the day time wherever I went. When they came out of school I'd take them out you see - the shops used to keep open 'til nine o'clock at night in those days.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So if you went out in the evening you'd go by yourself would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 In the evening well I - if he wasn't there I would take the children with me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you let your children join in when grown ups were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. Definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did you bring them up to consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, they went to Sunday school, they went to the Band of Hope and they would - I used to run a Band of Hope with about ninety children at High Path Road Mission. Yes, and they had to say their 
pieces you know - same as other children - and - do - and they went to Sunday School - with - a - Mrs - Mrs Wilson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you tell them they should hit back or not if another child hurt them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, - I told them that they could come and tell me th
at - they wasn't to fight - they'd come and tell me and - what was wrong and I would see into it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were there any other children you discouraged them from playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Never, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 If your children did something you disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, I can't - I can't say there was much - they were very good children - they were brought up the right way you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were they punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, not if they did - if they did anything out of the ordinary they may have to to to bed but nothing else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You would send them to bed - not your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no, he never did nothing with the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would that happen often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, very very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Do you remember any particular occasion when you punished them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would you say that your children received the ideas they had about how to behave from both parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, they would get it - certain amount from their father but it was chiefly me. Because he worked long hours in those days because it was the war and he was not home much you see. Just to sleep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When you worked before the children went to school I think you said that you had people in at home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 So you didn't have to leave them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. That was the mothers and babies from the clinic in London. Marylebone clinic in London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Some people think that children should be with the mother all the time - others think it's not necessary and does them good to be with other people quit a lot too what did you think at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, no, I don't hold with that - I believe that the mothers the right person to be responsible for her children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 When your children had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh I'd give them a little party - a few of their school friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did they receive presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, little things you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would they have a special tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. We'd have a little - little extra as far as I could go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Can you remember anything you did with your husband and children on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well - no - nothing particular. We - used to fill their stocking up you know on Christmas Eve and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Er - now then what did we have. Oh I had - I had the piano - second hand one I bought and - we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Only a little bit by ear. 'Cos dad had an organ and I'd do a little bit with that by ear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the others play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh no. Well, I started the girl at - learning the piano but - tele
vision - wireless coming up - no television - wireless cane along and that crushed it. Then we had a wireless you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did any of you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh now, well I was in the choir at Manor Road - I used to take my children Sunday evenings and - with me 
- I always took them - my husband used to go to his club but I always took the children. One time we filled a whole row in Manor Road Mission with us - his people - his mother and father and sisters - mothers and me and my husband and my children and so o
n
 but - they all crept into the club with him and things went a little bit awkward. So, of course we - but I was in the - Mr Hutchings - I don't know if you've ever heard the name - he started the - yellow bus service - and - Mr Hutchings and Mr Hater ran 
t
he yellow buses - well from Stoughton to Guildford. But Mr Hutchings was - a man that was in the choir at the Manor Road Mission and he played the organ and he would - not run the bus service on the Sunday. And that was the smashing up of the yellow bus s
ervice. So ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about making music together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, we'd sing together - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you play games with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, definitely
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did your husband join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes. He would play games when he was in - oh yes. Darts and all that sort of thing you know - ordinary games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were there books, magazines, newspapers in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, I don't think I - used to get one when I went out you see, I didn't have anybody regularly calling for that. Same as his.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Where did you get them from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Newspaper shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you belong to a library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you read aloud to each other or to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, I didn't do that - I'm afraid my time was fully occupied. Because I used to help with the b
abies of these mothers you see, I used to put them on the right track 'cos I had one or two slack ones you know in my time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Were the children taken out visiting neighbours or friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, no, in school days - I took them out on my
 own when they were - before they went to school - in school days time they come home and that they - they would be at home you see, I wouldn't take them out to to......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever take them shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh well, when - holidays and when they couldn't be at school - yes definite.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the children ever go out with just their father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did you do on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh we'd go all out together on Bank Holidays. Except he had an hour or two in his club in the evening. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, only days out in them days. I never went away for a holiday with the children - well, we did go to Malvern once or twice. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Not very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 No, not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And you went to see your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, they were at Malvern you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you all go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, when we went there we'd all go together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What would you do when you got there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, go out and enjoy ourselves - might go about walking. And go out on the hills
 you know 'cos Malvern's very hilly place. I expect you know it don't you yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Saturdays - well, extra work I suppose - I - I don't know as any different much than any other day except - 
well - I really don't know 'cos you work average same every day didn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What about Sundays - would they be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh Sunday was different because of the Sunday school for the children and - and I used to go and my - when I had the mothers
 and babies you see, if the babies were too young to take well I would stay home and let them go with the other - with my children you see or something of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you or the children put on different clothes on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh generally had Sunday best.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you think it wrong to work or enjoy yourself on a Sunday - or did you think it didn't matter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, there wasn't really much chance of it - you might have an extra job or two to do on a Sunday like you - you couldn't fit in in the week sometimes you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You didn't think it wrong to work in principle on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Well, not your ordinary work - in the - no, not the home work. I wouldn't do anything - I - that wouldn't have appealed to Sunday - that wouldn't appeal to what a Sunday was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you allow your children to play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Only indoors - they played their games indoors - they wouldn't go out for - well not footballing and all that sort of thing - they wouldn't do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 I think you said you took them to Sunday School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Oh yes, I took them to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did they go to church as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Er - no - well, not - not when they were very young - they would be going to bed you see. Except - well - what age would it be - when they were very young I used to take them myself 'cos I was in the choir and they'd sit on the chair when I was there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Was this the Congregational Mission?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Er - yes - Mission chapel - in Manor Road - well it's not - it belongs to the Brethren now but it - in th
ose days it belonged to the Congregational.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 And that would be most Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Yes. I had one incident with my boy - he - one Sunday I had - heard that they were throwing their caps about in Sunday School so I thought well - go down and see what's 
happening. So I went down and I found it was correct what I'd heard so I said well my boy I said you don't go to Sunday School I said to throw your cap about so I said I'm going to take you away from there and give you a walk - you just go to Salvation Ar
m
y Sunday School. So he had to walk it from Stoughton to Guildford every Sunday for his Sunday School. So that was his punishment for doing what he shouldn't do. But he was there for - oh a number of years - he was - he had his - for - long service he had 
his Bible and all that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Would your husband go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
Oh, when - well, he went for a while but I say he got so thick down at this club - when the family went in - first - before the children come that really was, when I was on my own more -
 all the family - his side and mine used to go - we filled whole row in Manor Road Mission.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 You said you belonged to the choir didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did the Mission run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, that's where the children went I had a - children - nearly ninety and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 That was the club you were talking about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Yes, on the Monday we used to go down there - that was - belonged to the same chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 What did they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Well, they say their pieces you know, recitat
ions and we'd teach them choruses and all that sort of thing. A friend of mine used to play the organ and - and I'd look after the children and I - two old ladies that's passed on now - they used to sit amongst the boys - and they used to well make fun of
 - the boys used to of these old ladies. They used to say she hasn't got her eyes on - and see what the were doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13781051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Did you belong to any other clubs organised by the Mission?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5578324 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 Er - yes, the women}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5381203\charrsid10685554 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 s meeting - we all - on a Wednesday. And I used to - before I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 - 'cos I - you see I was in Colonel Anderson's - before I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403139 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14308090\charrsid10685554 
 that was in Manor Road in - I was cook for him - well, I used to go to the week night prayer meeting then.
